h4#controller-parameters Controller Parameters
table.params-table
  thead
    tr
      th Parameter
      th Type
      th Default
      th Description
  tbody
    tr
      td controller
      td object/boolean
      td
      td
        p Object with controller parameters or boolean <b>true</b> to enable with default settings. For example:
          pre
            code
              :code(lang="js")
                var mySwiper = new Swiper('.swiper-container', {
                  controller: {
                    inverse: true,
                  },
                });
    tr.subparam-open-row
      td(colspan="4") {
    tr.subparam-row
      td control
      td [Swiper Instance]
      td undefined
      td Pass here another Swiper instance or array with Swiper instances that should be controlled by this Swiper
    tr.subparam-row
      td inverse
      td boolean
      td false
      td Set to <b>true</b> and controlling will be in inverse direction
    tr.subparam-row
      td by
      td string
      td 'slide'
      td Can be <code>'slide'</code> or <code>'container'</code>. Defines a way how to control another slider: slide by slide (with respect to other slider's grid) or depending on all slides/container (depending on total slider percentage)
    tr.subparam-close-row
      td(colspan="4") }
